text: Islamgulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Zildyarovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 205 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 47 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 15 km from Zildyarovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Islamgulovo, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
